snippet.title: MaiMai Orange - Japanese arcade is amazing...
snippet.description:
Went to Japan this fall and played some maimai! One of the funnest rhythm game i've played and a one i actually like...cuz i suck at rhythm games. Used a GoPro 2014 Entry Level cam to test some low light situations. i think it's pretty good for a 120$ GoPro, worth!

If you liked the video, please leave a thumbs up!

All the credits for music/audio goes to the original creators.
